Description:
We challenged the Reddit community to build anything they could imagine using the GitHub Copilot SDK in just one weekend. The results were wild, from an autonomous agent playing Stardew Valley to a fully functional AI-powered web browser. Check out the top 10 submissions that push the boundaries of what Copilot can do.

#CopilotSDK #GitHubCopilot #GitHub
